Welcome to _Collider.JAM_!

_Collider.JAM_ is a hand-crafted JavaScript game framework for game jamming, creative coding, prototyping and beyond.

It is a fun way to prototype and create games.

_Collider.JAM_ conceals rough JavaScript edges,
turning development into a joyride.
It is the most pleasant way to learn JavaScript.
You don't have to worry about DOM, CSS and MVC frameworks here.

To start, check out <a href="#.getting-started">Getting Started</a>.

Collider.JAM keeps everything in the right place,
so it is crucial to know the structure.
Investigate <a href="#./">the root node</a>.

Also, check out useful <a href="#.tips">tips</a>.

